title: REWRITE
text:
This is the website of the RE-WRITE Working Group - REproducible Ways for Research In Transport Engineering.
We are a group of volunteers who are passionate of practicing and promoting reproducible research in Transport Engineering.

title: Get involved
text:
We always welcome new members to join the working group and contribute to the mission of promoting reproducible research in the transportation research community.
To express your interest, please contact Dr Zuduo Zheng at zuduo.zheng@uq.edu.au, or Dr Christine Buisson at Christine.BUISSON@entpe.fr.
